WEBVTT

00:00.019 --> 00:02.855
Previously on The Originals...
You said there was a way to save her.

00:02.897 --> 00:04.816
We pull the Hollow out of Hope
and I need a place that's

00:04.857 --> 00:07.110
connected to Hope to put it.
When the spell is over,

00:07.151 --> 00:08.611
you got to get away
from each other,

00:08.653 --> 00:10.071
and you have to stay away
from Hope.

00:10.113 --> 00:12.115
If the Mikaelsons come together

00:12.156 --> 00:15.118
it will signal darkness
like we've never known.

00:15.159 --> 00:17.370
Hayley's missing.

00:17.412 --> 00:18.538
I'll find your mother.

00:18.579 --> 00:20.707
And I swear
I'll return her to you.

00:20.748 --> 00:22.917
You see, Marcel,
my disease has always been

00:22.959 --> 00:24.752
blind devotion to my brother.

00:24.794 --> 00:26.462
I'm a danger to my family.

00:26.504 --> 00:28.756
So take away the memories.
Compel me.

00:28.798 --> 00:30.591
The promise of always and forever.

00:30.633 --> 00:32.552
Forget it. Let it go.

