00:50.111 --> 00:52.447
You know where you're going, hon?

00:53.990 --> 00:56.868
I ne... I need...

00:58.161 --> 01:00.121
food.

01:00.163 --> 01:02.832
Chicken and waffles,
two miles up the road.

01:02.874 --> 01:04.792
Good luck to you.

01:59.972 --> 02:01.891
Is there a problem?

02:08.689 --> 02:10.233
What is that?

02:10.274 --> 02:11.818
What is what?

02:14.403 --> 02:16.364
That noise.

02:16.405 --> 02:18.991
Okay, um...

02:19.033 --> 02:21.494
you look like
you could use some help.

02:26.999 --> 02:29.418
Hey. Yeah, I got a guy here
that, uh, just put his hand

02:29.460 --> 02:31.921
through our vending machine.
He just punched a hole in it.

02:47.728 --> 02:49.230
Come on!

02:49.272 --> 02:51.524
Aah!

